channel.title: CMD Commands, not working? :S
channel.description:
Hello.
I was about to do some fun with my commandprompt, but found out that it wasnt working! It says things like "this is not an internal or external commando, nor a program or program file". But I mean, I'm using normal stuff like "telnet", "ipconfig" and so on. Why? :S I installed JDK yesterday, can it have something to do with it? I have no idea but really wants to use my Commando thing. Anyone know why this is happening?
Thanks in advance..
